{"tid":280994,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[朱經偉律師，原來係黑警出身的大狀！]","createTime":"2017-06-12T11:41:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-18T10:27:46.000Z","uid":53379,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c6ffdbc7499c8a2d798b268975d0a09bbd8e9988","tid":280994,"uid":53379,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T11:41:08.000Z","msg":"[朱經偉律師，原來係黑警出身的大狀！]<br />\n<br />\n反黑組前高級督察彭彼德（ Peter Pannu 圖），他於94年因涉嫌收受「灣仔之虎」陳耀興賄款，要接受警隊紀律聆訊，斷斷續續停職7年，其間支取薪金高達400多萬元，彭彼德更善用停職時間，完成法律課程，並取得大律師資格。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HKComedian/posts/1321481751221336\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHKComedian%2Fposts%2F1321481751221336&d=XWf9e2y4pz2JN%2BxAH1OXP8n%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=38e70b6c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/HKComedian/posts/1321481751221336</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">停職高級督察變大律師<br />\n</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/640pix/20060630/Article_news/30la3p10.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2F640pix%2F20060630%2FArticle_news%2F30la3p10.jpg&h=82ab445b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n自97年起停職獲支全薪的督察林達明，其間獲得超過600萬元薪金；其實過去也有類似個案，當中來自警隊最長時間停職支全薪的個案，是反黑組前高級督察彭彼德（ Peter Pannu 圖），他於94年因涉嫌收受「灣仔之虎」陳耀興賄款，要接受警隊紀律聆訊，斷斷續續停職7年，其間支取薪金高達400多萬元，彭彼德更善用停職時間，完成法律課程，並取得大律師資格。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n另一名前高級督察劉國輝，先後因違反交通法例和非禮罪成，須接受警隊紀律聆訊，最後被勒令停職及不獲支薪，他入稟高院申請司法覆核，結果敗訴。劉國輝曾透露，警隊中其他被停職支全薪的個案，包括一名警長停職超過6年，總支薪200多萬元；一名高級警員停職2年，支全薪約60萬元。  <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20060630/6080802\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20060630%2F6080802&d=XWf9e2y4pz2JN%2BxAH1OXP8n%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=0c7a2f73\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20060630%2F6080802&h=aecb7bbc\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20060630/6080802</a>"},{"pid":"75fc96c7d9b055bc127273e5a634b5df4175ad63","tid":280994,"uid":63,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T11:42:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"902cb31ca2eeb98ae5d7912774dde5c2ceb94ff6","tid":280994,"uid":51753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T11:54:28.000Z","msg":"勵志"},{"pid":"dcdc17c9272b743590661a06892d1edbf6490b09","tid":280994,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T12:01:38.000Z","msg":"好似沈嘉偉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5cfb51b147f071eb487144b55e9373a799bb70f","tid":280994,"uid":42921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T12:48:01.000Z","msg":"犯法停職有糧出，聽到都扯扯地"},{"pid":"b9c0703de5a19d3908d2f9cda6e0b7cb5dde299a","tid":280994,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T13:17:17.000Z","msg":"原來係過來人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d38104e4a927f56e7f3bb6347436d5c154078339","tid":280994,"uid":17496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T13:24:40.000Z","msg":"咁都幾爽"},{"pid":"869e55b83c18e09d04fa8a45c5c0240a2973c083","tid":280994,"uid":38572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T13:52:00.000Z","msg":"律師咁易考? 定本身好撚勁"},{"pid":"8c2814001d2d0f3d5f93424387ba303e76391a70","tid":280994,"uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T13:55:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>律師咁易考? 定本身好撚勁</blockquote>垃圾都考到"},{"pid":"e2aa6e72792a386e99986d30db959a91bbb3d8d9","tid":280994,"uid":66283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T13:56:31.000Z","msg":"係又點，呢家個香港擺到明夾硬嚟"},{"pid":"6142c55a44762708b74ec09135456152d0199bd1","tid":280994,"uid":61271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTi